@NotNullDefault

Package com.github.tommyettinger.ds.support.sort

Code for customized sorting on primitive arrays and collections. This is Apache-licensed code from the FastUtil project with minimal changes.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FloatComparator
    A type-specific Comparator; provides methods to compare two primitive types both as objects and as primitive types.
    IntComparator
    A type-specific Comparator; provides methods to compare two primitive types both as objects and as primitive types.
    LongComparator
    A type-specific Comparator; provides methods to compare two primitive types both as objects and as primitive types.
  • Class Summary

    A class providing static methods and objects that do useful things with comparators.

    A type-specific comparator mimicking the natural order.

    FloatComparators.OppositeImplicitComparator
    A type-specific comparator mimicking the opposite of the natural order.
